{"tid":1021549,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"智慧監獄首季起運作　影像及智能手帶監視囚犯","createTime":"2019-02-14T10:19:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T10:47:16.000Z","uid":17646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"92719d9b28ecc18320ec90fd1c68b11a61abd2cd","tid":1021549,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T10:19:51.000Z","msg":"懲教署發展「智慧監獄」，開發多個系統包括維生指標監察系統、影像分析及監察系統和移動及位置監察系統。影像分析及監察系統主要用作監測在囚人士，防止自殺、自殘、打鬥及暈倒的異常或違規情況。署方正在壁屋監獄的4個囚倉安裝具新功能閉路電視，每個囚倉安裝12個鏡頭，今年第一季試用。署長胡英明指，人員巡查期間未能完全監視所有囚犯舉動，影像分析及監察能有所彌補。<br />\n<br />\n懲教署助理署長(服務質素)楊俊偉表示，亦計劃在羅湖懲教所試用智能手帶裝置，配合維生指標和移動及位置監察系統運作，囚犯佩戴智能手帶能監測其移動位置，同時能探測他們的心跳率，同於今年首季試行。<br />\n<br />\n胡又指去年成功搜獲毒品案25宗，包括16宗體內藏毒，署方將引入緝毒機械臂系統，搜索在囚人士吞食及排出的毒品，系統會自動偵測糞便位置，用清水沖射使其分解來取出毒品，預計今年第二季於荔枝角收押所試行。四個新系統成本約400萬港元。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190214/photo/bkn-20190214141102961-0214_00822_001_02b.jpg?20190214172429\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190214%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190214141102961-0214_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20190214172429&h=1a218904&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n署方在每個囚倉安裝12支閉路電視鏡頭。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190214/photo/bkn-20190214141102961-0214_00822_001_03b.jpg?20190214172429\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190214%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190214141102961-0214_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20190214172429&h=9b04ec23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n監察系統有助防止在囚人士自殺、自殘、打鬥及暈倒。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190214/photo/bkn-20190214141102961-0214_00822_001_04b.jpg?20190214172429\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190214%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190214141102961-0214_00822_001_04b.jpg%3F20190214172429&h=aa1cdb54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n署方將引入緝毒機械臂系統。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190214/bkn-20190214141102961-0214_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190214%2Fbkn-20190214141102961-0214_00822_001.html&d=ZfEq%2Fo1sgt4RLlfWMFNbDrAecByD1k%2Bs4QbbWwjAUoc%3D&h=8b77a000\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190214/bkn-20190214141102961-0214_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"50ac1a791973f305224051b066b82c9958c171da","tid":1021549,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T10:21:02.000Z","msg":"智能通櫃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f50a7afe554cc4af2f7997c262df68523d9ae43","tid":1021549,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50ac1a791973f305224051b066b82c9958c171da","tid":1021549,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T10:21:02.000Z","msg":"智能通櫃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T10:22:01.000Z","msg":"原來係射屎 唔係射屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8542afc212f7d3177f88005d3e95d2ac85c78219","tid":1021549,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f50a7afe554cc4af2f7997c262df68523d9ae43","tid":1021549,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50ac1a791973f305224051b066b82c9958c171da","tid":1021549,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T10:21:02.000Z","msg":"智能通櫃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T10:22:01.000Z","msg":"原來係射屎 唔係射屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T10:47:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}